NGEN README

C.Kachulis Feb. 9, 2015

NGEN is an open source software package for neutrino event generation.

To build, in setup.make set CXX to your desired compiler.

Then in this top directory, type "make".

This will install libraries into lib/, and copy headers into include/

example applications can be found in the examples/ directory.

For more information (User's Guide) see docs/ directory.
